Tell a short story of humanity with happy ending

Once upon a time, in a world where technology and nature coexisted in harmony, humanity had finally achieved its long-sought goal of world peace. 

The year was 2154, and the world was a utopia. Cities were powered by clean energy, pollution was a distant memory, and the air was fresh and clean. 

The once-blue skies were now a brilliant shade of cerulean, a sight that brought joy to the hearts of all who beheld it.
